Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.27,0:00:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now then, the 14 remaining Duelists who survived the Park Section
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}have broken through and are\N headed to the location of the next battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\pos(691,536)}The light from the blue sky\N overhead the stadium is enveloping them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\pos(643,538)}They go from the light to the\N pitch darkness of the Underground Section!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,14 of the Coasters survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yuma's among them, cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Bring it to 'em, Yuma!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yuma's in 14th place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's last place!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't meowter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.32,0:00:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a race, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The winner will be\N determined through a Duel in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.60,0:00:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they can't see anything in such a dark pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have no idea when a a flip side will reveal itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:01:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what traps await you, cat it to 'em, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well then, allow me to introduce to you the highlights of the Underground Section!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their aim is to decidedly defeat their opponents to determine the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the battlefields are...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Magma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Each of the four fields hold special characteristics.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, lure your opponents into the field that gives you the advantage during your Duels!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get fired up! Heart Burning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This will be true Hell, unlike before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who will survive...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, what scenery do you suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}awaits us on the other side of this hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, let's climb it together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too late for us to turn back now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come to combine\N together the power dwelling inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta release my Soul Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep running, keep running, until you get there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:03:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, once again, keep those challenges coming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My friends, keep on living in the here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep pressing onward together no matter what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear what Mr. Heartland said, Yuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(509,491)}"Number 53: The Fated Rail:\N Try Your Luck on a Trap Card?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Our aim in the Underground Section.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to decide which opponent we take down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you planning to fight against, Yuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(643,525)}Anyone's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(646,510)}I'm gonna do this. I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(653,510)}But there's only four fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(653,526)}That means only eight people can Duel there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Can't two groups clash at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's four fields, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two groups of four will start off, making eight people in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Eight people. It's eight. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Only eight people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... You {\i1}just{\i0} realized that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, how are we supposed to search for our opponents when it's this dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon. There's a map on the monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so you use this to figure out where the others are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've taken the lead in first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron is in second place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means Kaito will be third place if this pattern continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's waiting up ahead in this darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's throbbing with excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron, I'm the one who's going to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll raise my Life to the utmost maximum, and then I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IV! I'll catch up with you in no time at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear to defeat you in this section.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. Follow me, Ryouga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'll lure you right into the Magma Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ryouga... Your deck uses the Water Attribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have no chance of winning in the scorching hot Magma Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's the one who kidnapped Haruto before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was looking at the guy during\N the evening festival like he knew him well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His appearance matches the\N description Yuma gave me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to Droite,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the one manipulating those people who kidnapped Haruto from the background is that guy called Tron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}V... Tron... Those two are connected somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know why they kidnapped Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but I'll make you pay for dishonoring my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare ride in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The battles have begun at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Number 13, Burning Toramaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}has challenged Number 12, Gauche, to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kick the crap out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Wall Creator!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shut up! I'm not in the mood\N to play around with some small fry like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Heroic Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card lets me Special Summon\N a Heroic Challenger from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Warhammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's gonna be kicked about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Warhammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it ended just like that in an instant kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I expected no less from the former W.D.C. Operation Committee Member, Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not only does he have the looks going for him, he's got exceptional skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, show Yuma already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They started a battle over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! I gotta hurry and get a battle started!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, hit the breaks! There's a Trap Point up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, pay attention properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are! We got a nice mood going here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V, I challenge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it's Gauche yet again!\N This time he's challenging V to a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Show us a fiery battle this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heart Burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. You plan to fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:08:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warhammer! Attack him directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Radiance of Hell, from my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card negates a Monster's attack \Nand sends it back to the hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch, what a mood killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use our full power when you play such cheap little tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to use my full power against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Flames of Retribution!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If inflicts 600 points of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there! Now {\i1}Gauche{\i0} is {\i1}Burning{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-This may be a bit too much for all you good kids at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another battle has started in a separate location!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the Asian Champion, IV!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this started now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killer Knight, Direct Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On this side, Number 5, Ryouga, will begin his assault!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sick them, Big Jaws!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Chew!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Ryouga. Keep following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll guide you straight into Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IV's so strong! He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark's the stronger one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives? IV's the one who's been stronger and cooler all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Yuma's obviously the strongest and the coolest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- As if.\N - As if.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! If you go that way, another-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oof...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're not looking at all, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Observation #19...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma is truly an idiot... after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Magic Point up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my intuition is correct, it's likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God of Healing, Dian Keto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its effect increases my Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7000, huh? It's still not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need more Life in order to fight him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron stopped again... This movement...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orbital!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, Kaito-{\i0}sama{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number two's Coaster, Tron's, is moving suspiciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look into it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tron...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another Trap Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Trap Card, Poison of the Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Trap that will inflict 1000 points of damage unto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's Traps laid about all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where they're trying to lead me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are getting more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's still not enough... More... I need more Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you only have 200 points left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in trouble if they decrease any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like there's anything I can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing points during a Duel is one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but losing them because you fell into a Trap yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it couldn't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A Trap Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit the breaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Again{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Trap Card, The Paths of Destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You conduct a coin toss
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if it's heads, your Life Points increase by 2000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's tails, you take 2000 points of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2000 points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:12:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely gonna get heads and increase my points by 2000!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! If you get tails, your Life will be reduced to zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll recover the Life Points I lost myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured Yuma would say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's futile, no matter what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop wasting time babbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My spirit hasn't fallen yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been waiting for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the moment my Life fell down to 500!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Heroic Challenger - Double Lance from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one Monster can be treated as two Xyz Materials!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay my Level Four Double Lance treated as two Xyz Materials!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use this Monster twice to build the Overlay Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Heroic Challenger - Excalibur!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur can't attack unless my Life Points are 500 or lower!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that time is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I detach all its Overlay Units in order to double its Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Excalibur! Attack V directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Single Sword Strike: Sure-Kill Divine Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How laughable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.06,0:14:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Trap Card, Those Crawling Into Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card negates the attack of a Monster with 2000 or more Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:15:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the opposing player takes damage equal to half the Attack Power of that Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be cut down by the sword of his own comrade...\N I truly pity the fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use Achachacha Sword Fighter, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I Summon Achachacha Sword Fighter from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Achachacha Sword Fighter springs into action during Effect Damage and negates it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,inflicting 400 points of damage to the opposing player in the process!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My{\i0} Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, V, are you about to Summon a Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We still need to let him go for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuma! Why didn't you chase after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should also hold a grudge against V!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly than that for now, you need to focus on recovering your Life first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon and follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma Tsukumo... Is his aim victory or friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He resembles Kazama quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazama Tsukumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He valued friendship greatly.\N Perhaps that is what called forth his misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... a Trap Point?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You recovered Life Points with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:17:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! If you get heads in a coin toss, you get your hands on 2000 Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one surprising guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just gotta believe in your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you fail, your Life Points will be cut down by 2000 instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put all your fighting spirit into that coin toss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap! I fell behind again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, a Trap Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2950 Attack Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2700...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4200!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little old me up against three top-class Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three people with one strike...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how strong {\i1}is{\i0} Tron?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let Kaito fight with Tron...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so they press on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:19:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Out of the 23 Finalists, only 14 survived the Park Section.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so far in the Underground Section, six have dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That leaves us with eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma finally came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried he'd be knocked out, but to summarize, he did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the remaining group is incredibly strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma will be just fine!\N Cat it to 'em with all you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, starting now are the one-on-one Duels!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They are aiming for four of these Duel Fields!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go into battle, my warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heart Burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now follow after me, Ryouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this, I'll go do\N another coin toss and increase my Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! If you don't get heads next time, you'll only limit yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about fighting spirit! Bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A Trap Card?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct, Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron's strange movements
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were due to him stopping a series of Trap Cards in his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the set cards had "Butterfly" in their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butterfly cards...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tron is my prey! I won't let anyone else touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you after Tron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've sworn my allegiance to Mr. Heartland.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who it is, I will utterly crush anyone getting in his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here it is! This time it's Droite!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She is a former W.D.C. Operation Committee Member. Her Dueling skills are topnotch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance onward with the revived Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:21:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Droite has indeed sworn her allegiance to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But why would she get in Kaito's way...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go! I'm the one who's going to fight against Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will show you no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll return those words to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pay 1000 of my Life Points to activate the Continuous Magic Card, Dance of the Butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It inflicts 300 points of damage to my opponent for each card with "Butterfly" in its name in my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I reflexively changed my course...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live... Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Jungle Field is up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lure him out into the dense tropical forest, my deck will have the advantage,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my chances of winning will increase!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's the one who's been trying to lure me into a trap, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll take the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to fight me that badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... It's like it's a real jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.10,0:22:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the area you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.82,0:22:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The Jungle Field...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.69,0:22:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us alone will fight here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:23:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move on ahead, speeding up our throbbing beats
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen boys and girls, here's the secret to boys and girls like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really just so spontaneous, wild as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.69,0:23:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You might be a handful, but what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.28,0:23:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be up to no good, but learn for real
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.91,0:23:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go the unpredictable route and shuffle your cards with a goal in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.16,0:23:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever you feel like you've lost your way, just take a minute to close your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shout "stop!" with all you've got, and there's your boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just stop here, not when we don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.10,0:23:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we get hurt, we can't just hesitate now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.40,0:24:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just give up, not when our future's a lot brighter than our today
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriousness... It'll only make us keep fighting even harder
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.24,0:24:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always get as fascinated as we want, and we'll fight on every day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Duel Carnival Tournament Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.94,0:24:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite and the mysterious masked boy \Nduke it out in the Jungle Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.82,0:24:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Droite!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.11,0:24:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a perfect Magic Combo she utilized along with her Field Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.70,0:24:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of love... It's kind lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.16,0:24:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Number is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.58,0:24:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories? What the heck's that Tron guy up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.00,0:24:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.50,0:24:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tron vs Droite - Allure of the Death Butterfly!\N The Life-Threatening Jungle Field!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.46,0:24:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.30,0:24:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel Coasters are so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.01,0:24:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have the luxury to enjoy the Duel Coasters right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.01,0:24:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I bet they wouldn't hold a candle to Big Sis Akari's motorcycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.14,0:24:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motorcycle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.76,0:25:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, don't you think it's too much\N for Akari to just take off like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.31,0:25:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So now you're interested in the motorcycle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.81,0:25:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
